description: [Emotet](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0367) has used a self-extracting RAR file to deliver modules to victims. Emotet has also extracted embedded executables from files using hard-coded buffer offsets.(Citation: Binary Defense Emotes Wi-Fi Spreader)

external_references.description: Binary Defense. (n.d.). Emotet Evolves With new Wi-Fi Spreader. Retrieved September 8, 2023.
